---
title: Dukkah Beef Rump & Buttery Freekeh with Roasted Veggies & Lemon Yoghurt
description: If you haven't tried freekeh, give this colourful bowl a try. Stirring roasted veggies and spinach through this protein-rich ancient
grain brings it to life, while the addition of succulent dukkah beef rump delivers a nutritious meal everyone will love.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
